1. Create Recycler View Activity , with the RV in xml file

2. Create the card view layout in the layout res.

3. Create the model class.

4. Create the RV adapter
        A. Make the adapter extends RecyclerView.Adapter.
        B. Create a view holder .. public class ViewHolder extends RecyclerView.ViewHolder.
        C. RecyclerView.Adapter<RVAdapter.ViewHolder>.
        D. import the Override Methods ( onCreateViewHolder, onBindViewHolder, getItemCount).
        E. in RvActivity set the RV & the adapter.


